General '''Hong Dalson'''([[hangul]]:홍달손, [[hanja]]:洪達孫, 1415–72) was a Korean [[Joseon Dynasty]] politician and soldier. He served [[Sejo of Joseon|King Sejo]],<ref>[http://100.daum.net/encyclopedia/view.do?docid=b25h1932a Hong Dalson] {{ko}}</ref> and was viceprime minister of [[Joseon Dynasty]]s from 1467 to 1472. His [[courtesy name]] was '''Gachik'''(가칙 可則). and his title was '''Grand duke of Namyang'''<ref>[http://koreandb.nate.com/history/people/detail?sn=13902 Hong Dalson] {{ko}}</ref>

