*[[Angus Charles Graham|A. C. Graham]] (1981), ''Chuang-tzu, The Seven Inner Chapters and Other Writings from the Book Chuang-tzu'', London: George Allen and Unwin.  Translation notes published separately in 1982 as ''Chuang-tzu: Textual Notes to a Partial Translation'', London: School of Oriental and African Studies.
*[[Victor H. Mair]] (1994), ''Wandering on the Way: Early Taoist Tales and Parables of Chuang Tzu'', New York: Bantam Books; republished (1997), Honolulu: University of Hawaii Press.
